# System tecture: RSS News Digest System

The **RSS News Digest System** is a modular, AI-powered news aggregator, analyzer, summarizer, and delivery platform. It consists of an automated ingestion/analysis pipeline running on a background scheduler, a local SQLite database, and an interactive Streamlit-based web dashboard.

